    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ancient Greek warships propelled by 25 pairs of oarsmen; such ships formed the backbone of early Greek naval fleets.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
